{"type": "article", "id": 2611, "title": "木条编织家具", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-28T08:40:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232311MnVFPovNgEqx3B5r.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国设计师 Sebastian Cox 日前联手木材加工技术方面的专家 Lorna Singleton ，运用特色编织技术，在今年的<a href=\"http://www.londondesignfestival.com/\" target=\"_blank\">伦敦设计节</a>上推出了一系列编织木条家具 Swill 系列。制作过程中先要将整块木材削成条状，再放进煮沸的水里进行软化，经过处理后，才能将其编织成板凳、架子以及吊灯等，呈现出简单的结构美学。定价 75-595 英镑不等，<a href=\"http://sebastiancox.co.uk/collections/swill\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232309e9LZJyQoH84D3Pgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232310X82TAuUrGk6Ep01L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323102QS3rbWEp9ncUl6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232310Fvueoqjc8kgXSl7w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}